Order Online View Menu Our Story 
Crab Du Jour offers experience-driven seafood dining in a fun, communal atmosphere, perfect for friends and family.
 
Our Cajun-inspired eatery is known for fresh seafood boils (made for sharing) and an array of signature house-blended sauces, to enhance the experience.
 
We offer everything from delicious starters like wings, po-boys, chicken tenders, and seafood favorites such as fried fish, shrimp, crab and oysters.
